+# Exploration 003 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Screen the frozen package against the nearest prior-art families and recommend
+the Step-11 verdict from local repository evidence only.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the Step-11 goal, canonical chain, run-007 planning and judgment
+  materials, prior exploration outputs, receptionist packet, exact-NS Tao
+  comparison reports, and packet-policy factual files.
+- Compare the frozen package to Waleffe-type triad analysis, helical
+  decimation, shell-model intuition, and same-helicity favorable-sector lore.
+- Label major claims `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, or `[PROPOSED]`.
+
+## Working Notes
+
+### Initial orientation
+
+- Exploration 001 already reports that the branch is narrowed to a provisional
+  `stretching/enstrophy bottleneck` + `dyadic coupled fluxes` + `role-labeled
+  helical packet Tao screen`, but fails to freeze a baseline criterion or
+  minimum gain threshold.
+- Exploration 002 already reports that the exact ledger lives at the
+  Fourier/Leray helical-triad core and that the Tao screen is operational but
+  exact-but-noncoercive on local evidence.
+
+## Source Findings
+
+### Pending source extraction
+
+- To be filled from the named run-007, CHAIN, receptionist, atlas-source, and
+  factual packet documents.
+
+## Provisional Verdict
+
+- Pending. Earlier explorations suggest a negative verdict, but the precise
+  Step-11 obstruction label still needs source-backed comparison against the
+  nearest prior-art families.

