+
+## Working Notes
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exploration 001 already narrowed the branch to a provisional
+  package:
+  `stretching/enstrophy bottleneck` +
+  `dyadic coupled fluxes` +
+  `role-labeled helical packet Tao screen`,
+  but it also found that the baseline cash-out and minimum gain threshold were
+  not frozen concretely enough.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exploration 002 already showed that the exact ledger lives only
+  at the Fourier/Leray helical-triad core, that the dyadic package is only an
+  aggregation of that core, and that the Tao screen is operational but yields
+  no theorem-facing one-sided gain.
+
+## Verdict First
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Recommended Step-11 verdict:
+  `prior-art overlap obstruction + calibration obstruction, branch should stop before coercivity gate`.
+- `[INFERRED]` First decisive obstruction:
+  `prior-art overlap obstruction`.
+  Once the package is written in its most honest exact form, its transfer
+  content sits inside helical-triad conservation/rigidity plus dyadic
+  reindexing, while every favorable-sector reading is explicitly disqualified
+  unless it carries a quantified burden share.
+- `[INFERRED]` `calibration obstruction` is stacked rather than primary.
+  The record does contain one genuine NS-sensitive discriminator
+  (packet-complete role bookkeeping with spectator leakage), but it does not
+  calibrate into a one-sided stretching/enstrophy gain, baseline improvement,
+  or Step-2-ready freeze.
+
+## Prior-Art Screen
+
+### Frozen package being screened
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The frozen package to screen is the best-supported provisional
+  one from explorations 001-002:
+  `stretching/enstrophy bottleneck` +
+  `dyadic coupled fluxes` +
+  `role-labeled helical packet Tao screen`.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The repository does not contain a standalone exact dyadic
+  energy/helicity identity sheet for this package, nor a frozen baseline
+  inequality or minimum quantitative threshold.
+- `[INFERRED]` The package therefore has to be judged in the most conservative
+  local form:
+  exact helical-triad ledger first, dyadic aggregation second.
+
+### Waleffe-type triad analysis
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exploration 002 states that the sharpest exact transfer ledger
+  available locally is the helical-triad core:
+  exact triads `p + q = k`,
+  exact Leray projection,
+  cyclic energy/helicity conservation constraints,
+  and mandatory conjugate completion.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The same exploration also states that `dyadic coupled fluxes`
+  are exact only as an aggregation of that helical-triad ledger, not as a new
+  invariant identity.
+- `[INFERRED]` Relative to Waleffe-type triad analysis, the frozen package is
+  therefore not theorem-distinct in its exact transfer mathematics.
+  Its exact content is triad-rigidity/sign bookkeeping with a dyadic relabel.
+- `[INFERRED]` The only extra ingredient is the packet/Tao comparison
+  discipline:
+  fixed role labels,
+  sign/phase sheet,
+  conjugate completion,
+  and spectator leakage.
+  That is a real screening refinement, but it is not a new one-sided burden
+  law.
+
+### Helical decimation
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` `CHAIN.md`, `refined/chain-03.md`, and exploration 001 all say
+  that favorable same-helicity or polarized sectors do not count unless they
+  carry a quantitatively relevant share of the full burden after
+  mixed-helicity restoration.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The selected and refined chain also say the branch should be
+  killed if it works only in decimated, filtered, or strongly polarized
+  sectors.
+- `[INFERRED]` Relative to helical decimation, the frozen package is distinct
+  only negatively:
+  it insists on full packet completion and full-equation restoration.
+- `[INFERRED]` No positive burden-level gain survives that restoration on the
+  present record.
+  So any attractive same-sign transfer story still collapses into
+  decimation-adjacent lore once the branch's own novelty rule is enforced.
+
+### Shell-model intuition
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The Tao screen requires more than a sparse or multiscale shell
+  picture:
+  identifiable roles,
+  ordered delayed-threshold sequence,
+  dominant-channel hierarchy,
+  tight sign/phase bookkeeping,
+  and bounded spectator leakage.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The Tao screen also says that a family that is merely sparse,
+  multiscale, or triad-engineered should not count as Tao-like.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exploration 002 uses generic same-helicity or shell-model
+  folklore as the failing calibration example.
+- `[INFERRED]` Relative to shell-model intuition, the frozen package again has
+  only an obstruction-level distinction:
+  exact NS forces triad rigidity and spectator leakage where Tao-style shell
+  circuits want tunable isolated gates.
+- `[INFERRED]` That distinction improves the honesty of the audit, not the
+  strength of the theorem-facing package.
+  Since the dyadic package is only shell aggregation of the triad core, shell
+  language does not create a new burden-level object.
+
+### Same-helicity favorable-sector lore
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The canonical chain and explorations 001-002 say that
+  same-helicity or polarized sectors are novelty failures unless they are
+  packet-complete and burden-relevant after mixed-helicity restoration.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The repository contains no source-backed result showing that a
+  favorable same-helicity sector carries a quantitatively relevant portion of
+  the full stretching/enstrophy burden.
+- `[INFERRED]` Relative to same-helicity favorable-sector lore, the frozen
+  package does not earn a positive theorem distinction.
+  It earns only a stronger refusal to count favorable-sector rhetoric as
+  progress.
+- `[INFERRED]` At theorem-facing burden level this means collapse, not
+  survival:
+  the favorable-sector story is prior-art-adjacent, while the packet/Tao
+  discipline that filters it remains non-coercive.
+
+## Distinctness Assessment
+
+### What is genuinely distinct on this record
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The record supports one real NS-sensitive feature beyond
+  generic shell or same-helicity folklore:
+  a role-labeled helical packet with mandatory conjugate completion, explicit
+  sign/amplitude/phase sheet, and spectator-leakage discipline, tested against
+  the five-part Tao canonicalization screen.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Exploration 002 shows that this feature passes the local Tao
+  screen, while generic same-helicity or shell-model folklore fails it.
+- `[INFERRED]` So the package is not literally identical to prior-art rhetoric
+  at the level of comparison protocol.
+
+### Why that distinctness does not save the branch
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The same record also says that the exact ledger remains
+  exact-but-noncoercive, that no standalone dyadic identity sheet is frozen,
+  and that no one-sided stretching/enstrophy cash-out or quantitative gain
+  threshold has been fixed.
+- `[VERIFIED]` `CHAIN.md`, the run-007 judgment packet, and exploration 001
+  all require theorem-facing distinction to cash out as one named bad-term or
+  bad-transfer-pattern improvement on a quantitatively relevant burden share.
+- `[INFERRED]` The packet/Tao distinction does not meet that burden.
+  It distinguishes exact NS from Tao-style averaging as an obstruction story,
+  but not as a one-sided mechanism that beats Waleffe/decimation/shell
+  folklore at the stretching/enstrophy interface.
+- `[INFERRED]` Therefore the frozen package does **not** stay distinct at
+  theorem-facing burden level.
+  It collapses into sign-sensitive but non-coercive cascade bookkeeping, with
+  a stricter comparison discipline than ordinary folklore but no stronger
+  endpoint leverage.
+
+## Typed Obstruction Or Clearance
+
+### Status of the substantive claims
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The Tao calibration is operational.
+  This is not a failure to define a pass/fail screen.
+- `[VERIFIED]` The exact transfer ledger is recoverable only at the
+  helical-triad core, with dyadic fluxes honest only as aggregation.
+- `[VERIFIED]` No source-backed theorem-facing one-sided gain has been frozen.
+- `[VERIFIED]` No source-backed burden-share estimate rescues same-helicity,
+  polarized, decimated, or shell-style favorable sectors.
+
+### Narrowest honest failure label
+
+- `[INFERRED]` The sharpest stacked label is:
+  `prior-art overlap obstruction + calibration obstruction`.
+- `[INFERRED]` Why `prior-art overlap obstruction` comes first:
+  once the package is written honestly, its exact mathematical content is
+  triad-rigidity/sign bookkeeping already adjacent to Waleffe/helical/shell
+  families, and the branch's own novelty rule rejects favorable sectors that
+  fail burden-share accounting.
+- `[INFERRED]` Why `calibration obstruction` remains stacked:
+  the residual packet/Tao distinctness is real, but it does not calibrate into
+  a Step-2-ready bad-term reduction, baseline improvement, or quantitative
+  threshold.
+- `[VERIFIED]` `setup obstruction` is not the best top label for this
+  exploration.
+  The scope lock and Tao memo are already concrete enough to screen the
+  package honestly; the decisive new failure is the collapse of theorem-facing
+  distinctness under prior-art and burden-level scrutiny.
+
+## Step-2 Freeze If Any
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` No positive Step-2 freeze is earned.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Step 2 is **not** allowed to proceed on a claim that the frozen
+  package is a distinct coercivity candidate.
+- `[INFERRED]` The only honest carry-forward without changing terms is
+  negative:
+  Step 11 may freeze the package only as an obstruction dossier saying that
+  the exact helical-triad/dyadic packet with Tao-sensitive spectator
+  discipline is real but non-coercive and prior-art-adjacent at theorem-facing
+  burden level.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Under the Step-11 verdict menu, that means the branch should
+  stop before coercivity testing rather than enter Step 2 with a live positive
+  package.
+
+## Failed Attempts / Dead Ends
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` I looked for a local source that upgraded `dyadic coupled
+  fluxes` into a standalone exact invariant identity beyond triad aggregation.
+  None was found.
+- `[VERIFIED]` I looked for a local source that quantified a theorem-relevant
+  burden share for same-helicity or polarized favorable sectors.
+  None was found.
+- `[VERIFIED]` I looked for a local source that converted the packet/Tao
+  distinction into a one-sided stretching/enstrophy inequality or exclusion
+  statement.
+  None was found.
+
+## Final Recommendation
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Step-11 verdict recommendation:
+  `prior-art overlap obstruction + calibration obstruction, branch should stop before coercivity gate`.

